---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const calendlyUrl = 'https://calendly.com/zaxkalyan/new-meeting';

const firstSystemPrinciples = [
	{
		title: 'It should solve a real business problem.',
		copy: 'The recommendation should be tied to a real operational pressure, not an AI idea looking for somewhere to fit.',
	},
	{
		title: 'It should fit the way your team already works.',
		copy: 'The best first system should support the way the business already runs, rather than forcing people into a completely new process.',
	},
	{
		title: 'It should have a clear reason to exist before anything is built.',
		copy: 'Before build work starts, there should be a clear business reason, expected value, and practical use case.',
	},
];

const deliverables = [
	'A 30-minute discovery and workflow review.',
	'A 30-minute blueprint presentation.',
	'A review of your current way of working, tools, bottlenecks and manual pressure points.',
	'A clear map of where AI can create the most value in your business.',
	'A recommended first system to build, with a clear reason why.',
	'A practical value view, so you can see where the return can come from.',
	'A written blueprint you keep, specific to your business and not a generic template.',
];

const proofPoints = [
	{
		title: 'Spa by Kaajal',
		copy: 'A finance admin and visibility system that reduced weekly finance admin from around 4 hours to around 30 minutes, with invoices, receipts, tips, missing items and accountant-ready exports in one place.',
	},
	{
		title: 'Jas’s School of Spice',
		copy: 'A booking and operations system for cookery classes, covering bookings, payments, vouchers, reminders, customer communication, owner alerts and protected operations management.',
	},
	{
		title: 'Kalyan AI internal systems',
		copy: 'Kalyan AI also runs its own business through controlled AI systems for managing relationships, outreach, reminders, reporting and owner visibility.',
	},
];
---

<Layout
	title="Business AI Blueprint | Kalyan AI"
	description="A focused review showing where AI can make your business easier to run and grow, what system would be worth building first, and where the return can come from."
	showFinalCta={false}
>
	<main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 pb-16">
		<section class="ka-card mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-5 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--primary)] bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[var(--brand-navy)]">
				Focused paid review
			</p>
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)] md:text-5xl">Business AI Blueprint</h1>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] md:text-lg">
				A focused review showing where AI can make your business easier to run and grow, what system would be worth building first, and where the return can come from.
			</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--primary)]">
				Built by Kalyan AI, a team that designs, builds, deploys and supports production-grade AI systems around how businesses actually work.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
				<a
					class="rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
					href={calendlyUrl}
					data-plausible="BookACall"
				>
					Book your Blueprint
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">A focused paid review</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
				The Business AI Blueprint is designed to give you clear, practical direction before committing to a larger AI system build.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Why business owners book a Blueprint</h2>
			<div class="copy-narrow mx-auto space-y-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
				<p>Business owners usually do not need another AI opinion. They need clarity.</p>
				<p>The Business AI Blueprint is for when you can see that AI could help, but you are not yet clear where it fits, what would be worth building first, or whether the return would justify the investment.</p>
				<p>It helps you step back from the day-to-day and look at how your business actually runs: where time is being lost, where decisions are being made without the full picture, where important things can slip, and where AI could make the business easier to run and grow.</p>
				<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">You do not need to know what system you need before we speak. That is the point of the Blueprint.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Why we start with a Blueprint</h2>
			<div class="copy-narrow mx-auto space-y-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
				<p>We do not start by selling a fixed product.</p>
				<p>Every business works differently, so the first step is to understand how yours actually runs. The Blueprint shows where AI can create the most value, what system would be worth building first, and whether there is a clear business case before anything is built.</p>
				<p>It gives you clarity before committing to a larger project.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">The right first system</h2>
			<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
				{firstSystemPrinciples.map((principle, index) => (
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/70 p-4 text-left shadow-sm">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Principle {index + 1}</p>
						<h3 class="mt-1 text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">{principle.title}</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-[var(--muted)]">{principle.copy}</p>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What you get</h2>
			<ul class="mx-auto grid max-w-4xl gap-3 text-left text-[var(--muted)] md:grid-cols-2">
				{deliverables.map((item) => (
					<li class="flex items-start gap-3 rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/70 p-4 shadow-sm">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span>
						<span>{item}</span>
					</li>
				))}
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Built from real delivery experience</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
					Kalyan AI builds systems around how real businesses actually work. The Blueprint is not theory. It comes from the same delivery approach used to build working systems for real business operations.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
				{proofPoints.map((proof) => (
					<div class="rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/70 p-4 text-left shadow-sm">
						<h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">{proof.title}</h3>
						<p class="mt-2 text-[var(--muted)]">{proof.copy}</p>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What happens after the Blueprint</h2>
			<div class="copy-narrow mx-auto space-y-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
				<p>After the Blueprint, you will have a clear view of where AI can help your business and what system would be worth building first.</p>
				<p>There is no obligation to continue. If there is a strong business case and you want Kalyan AI to build the recommended system, we can discuss the next step from there.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-5 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Ready to see where AI fits in your business?</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">
				Book your Business AI Blueprint and we will show you where AI can create the most value in your business, what system would be worth building first, and where the return can come from.
			</p>
			<a
				class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
				href={calendlyUrl}
				data-plausible="BookACall"
			>
				Book your Business AI Blueprint
			</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
